results.name: Sum of composite divisors of n that are not primes nor prime powers.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..65537
maple: pp := array(1..100); for i from 1 to 100 do pp[i] := 0; od: for i from 1 to 25 do for j from 1 to 6 do t1 := ithprime(i)^j; if t1<100 then pp[t1] := 1; fi; od: od: pp[1] := 1; A035321 := proc(n) local i,d,t1,t2; t1 := 0; for d from 1 to n do if n mod d = 0 and pp[d] = 0 then t1 := t1+d; fi; od; t1; end;
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
